<para><programlisting filename=".cs"><codeline><highlight class="normal">(A<sp/>&gt;<sp/>B<sp/>AND<sp/>C<sp/>&lt;<sp/>D<sp/>?<sp/>TrueValue<sp/>:<sp/>FalseValue)</highlight></codeline>
